race.description: Mallee Big Screen Hire Mdn Plate
race.comment: HYDE PARK CORNER (6) has been good in two runs to date and looks to have found the perfect maiden to be breaking through. The debut in town was good before a close up fifth at Bendigo. He just needs to hold a spot from the gate to be winning. HONEY MAKER (3) wasn't far away first up here when in the market over 1009m. That trip was always going to be sharp so rising to 1200m should suit and she can be competitive. ZEAMAIZE (2) has just found one better at all three runs this time in, good again out to 1400m last time. Back in trip here but he draws well and will be strong late. MONIX (1) is knocking on the door of late over shorter trips. Slight query to 1200m but can give cheek. OF THE VIEW (4) resumes and will get further but has the ability.
